Five people were injured after a shoot-out occurred at the Van Dyks Drift and Goedehoop Road intersection outside Witbank in Mpumalanga on Thursday.On arrival ER24 paramedics found five vehicles on the scene. One of the vehicle that was involved in the incident was a large cash-in-transit vehicle.Four patients sustained minor injuries while a fifth patient sustained a gunshot wound to his leg.Paramedics treated all patients on scene and thereafter transported them to hospitals in Witbank for further treatment.-TNA Reporter